-- MOVES-Mayfair Capital appoints Jonathan Gibbon investment director
-- 
-- Wed Jul 23, 2014 05:39AM EDT
-- None



July 23 (Reuters) - UK real estate investment manager Mayfair Capital Investment Management appointed Jonathan Gibbon as investment director.

Mayfair said Gibbon will work alongside Guy Brogden, head of investment and a co-founder of the firm, in leading the firm's transaction business.